    <p>
      The Tiny Happy People texting programme is designed to offer parenting support and a journey tailored to your family’s unique needs, with texts at a time most convenient for parents and their busy schedules. Each activity is from BBC Education’s catalogue of Tiny Happy People videos, designed by experts to support your child’s language and learning and strengthen your bond with your child.
